<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AI Gateway - Unified AI Infrastructure</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        brandPrimary: '#111CA8',
                        brandAccent: '#DE6A2C',
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
    <style>
        .gradient-hero-text {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #111CA8 30%, #DE6A2C 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        .cta-gradient {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #111CA8 0%, #1a29cc 100%);
        }
        .bg-grid-pattern {
            background-size: 30px 30px;
            background-image: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(17, 28, 168, 0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
                              linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(17, 28, 168, 0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 font-sans antialiased text-slate-900 selection:bg-orange-200">

    {{> public_header }}

    <main class="min-h-screen">
        <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-white border-b border-slate-100 bg-grid-pattern py-24 lg:py-32">
            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-gradient-to-bl from-orange-100/40 to-indigo-100/20 rounded-full filter blur-3xl -z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
            
            <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative">
                <div class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                    <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold text-orange-700 bg-orange-50 rounded-full border border-orange-200 mb-6">
                        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brandAccent animate-pulse"></span> Production Ready v2.0
                    </span>
                    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-8 tracking-tight leading-[1.1]">
                        Unified API for <br>
                        <span class="gradient-hero-text">Leading AI Models</span>
                    </h1>
                    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-600 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                        Access OpenAI, Anthropic, Gemini, and Mistral through a single production-grade pipeline. Built for scaling modern engineering teams.
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
                        <a href="/auth/register" class="w-full sm:w-auto text-center font-semibold text-white px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl shadow-lg transition-all duration-200 hover:scale-[1.02]" style="background-color: #111CA8; shadow-color: rgba(17, 28, 168, 0.3);">
                            Get Started Free <i class="fas fa-arrow-right ml-2 text-sm"></i>
                        </a>
                        <a href="/docs" class="w-full sm:w-auto text-center border border-slate-200 bg-white text-slate-700 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-semibold hover:bg-slate-50 hover:border-slate-300 transition-all duration-200">
                            View Documentation
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-20 p-6 bg-white border border-slate-200/60 rounded-2xl shadow-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto backdrop-blur-sm bg-opacity-80">
                        <div class="text-center p-4">
                            <div class="text-4xl font-extrabold" style="color: #111CA8;">4+</div>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium mt-1">Core Providers Injected</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-center p-4 border-y sm:border-y-0 sm:border-x border-slate-100">
                            <div class="text-4xl font-extrabold" style="color: #111CA8;">99.99%</div>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium mt-1">Guaranteed Uptime</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-center p-4">
                            <div class="text-4xl font-extrabold" style="color: #DE6A2C;">&lt;100ms</div>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium mt-1">Global Core Latency</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="py-24 bg-slate-50">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
                <div class="text-center mb-20">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 tracking-tight">
                        Why Engineers Choose AI Gateway
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-xl mx-auto">
                        Enterprise-ready layer designed to streamline continuous AI deployments.
                    </p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                    <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200/80 rounded-2xl p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl group">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 transition-colors" style="background-color: rgba(17, 28, 168, 0.06);">
                            <i class="fas fa-bolt text-xl transition-transform group-hover:scale-110" style="color: #111CA8;"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Fast & Reliable</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">Low latency proxy responses backed with fallback routines and dynamic routing policies.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200/80 rounded-2xl p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl group">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 transition-colors" style="background-color: rgba(222, 106, 44, 0.06);">
                            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt text-xl transition-transform group-hover:scale-110" style="color: #DE6A2C;"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Secure by Default</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">Keys encrypted strictly at rest with secure token isolation, internal rate limiting, and parameter checking.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200/80 rounded-2xl p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl group">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 transition-colors" style="background-color: rgba(17, 28, 168, 0.06);">
                            <i class="fas fa-chart-line text-xl transition-transform group-hover:scale-110" style="color: #111CA8;"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Usage Analytics</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">Deep tracking over metrics, compute consumption, prompt tokens, context window overhead, and real-time outlays.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200/80 rounded-2xl p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl group">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 transition-colors" style="background-color: rgba(222, 106, 44, 0.06);">
                            <i class="fas fa-code text-xl transition-transform group-hover:scale-110" style="color: #DE6A2C;"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Easy Integration</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">Native drop-in interface engine ready for custom configurations using standard JS, Python runtime modules.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200/80 rounded-2xl p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl group">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 transition-colors" style="background-color: rgba(17, 28, 168, 0.06);">
                            <i class="fas fa-dollar-sign text-xl transition-transform group-hover:scale-110" style="color: #111CA8;"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Cost Optimization</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">Automated dynamic runtime engine execution pathways optimized for minimizing structural API billings.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200/80 rounded-2xl p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl group">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 transition-colors" style="background-color: rgba(222, 106, 44, 0.06);">
                            <i class="fas fa-cloud-upload-alt text-xl transition-transform group-hover:scale-110" style="color: #DE6A2C;"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Multi-Modal Base</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">Native cross-functional handling for vectors, system audio, production matrices, structures, and dense token patterns.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="py-24 bg-white">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
                <div class="text-center mb-16">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 tracking-tight">Supported Native Frameworks</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 max-w-md mx-auto text-sm">Plug models seamlessly without custom structural adaptations.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
                    <div class="p-6 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl hover:border-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-100/50 transition-all text-center">
                        <i class="fab fa-openai text-4xl text-slate-800 mb-3 block"></i>
                        <span class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-sm">OpenAI</span>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">GPT-4o, o1</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-6 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl hover:border-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-100/50 transition-all text-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-robot text-4xl text-slate-700 mb-3 block"></i>
                        <span class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-sm">Anthropic</span>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">Claude 3.5 Sonnet</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-6 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl hover:border-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-100/50 transition-all text-center">
                        <i class="fab fa-google text-4xl text-blue-600 mb-3 block"></i>
                        <span class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-sm">Google Gemini</span>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">Gemini 1.5 Pro</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-6 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl hover:border-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-100/50 transition-all text-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-wind text-4xl text-sky-500 mb-3 block"></i>
                        <span class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-sm">Mistral AI</span>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">Mistral Large 2</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="py-24 text-white relative overflow-hidden" style="background-color: #111CA8;">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 bg-grid-pattern"></div>
            <div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center relative z-10">
                <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-4 tracking-tight">Ready to integrate?</h2>
                <p class="text-indigo-100 mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto font-medium">
                    Provision global enterprise access setups inside single modular routing contexts within 5 minutes.
                </p>
                <a href="/auth/register" class="bg-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold shadow-xl transition-all duration-200 hover:scale-105 inline-block" style="color: #111CA8;">
                    Create Account Free <i class="fas fa-arrow-right ml-2 text-xs"></i>
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-slate-900 border-t border-slate-800 py-12 text-center text-xs text-slate-400">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
            <p class="mb-2">© 2026 AI Gateway - All rights reserved • Secured by OIDC SSO</p>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Enterprise Orchestration Infrastructure</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>